[gd_scene load_steps=32 format=3]

; Dev-only greybox for the task-07 manual playtest (F6). Not wired into GameManager (mission flow is
; task 11). Each obstacle is an Obstacle (Interactable) Node3D with a StaticBody3D collider so the
; player's interaction ray resolves it; the MinigameHost node attaches to them all (via the Debug
; node) and mounts the right overlay on minigame_requested. Move WASD, look mouse, aim the + and press
; [F] (NOT E/Q — those are lean). Then drive the overlay with ◄►/▲▼ + [Enter], [Esc] to cancel:
;   * LOCK  -> lockpick (spin to the give, set; a miss can snap a pick)
;   * SAFE  -> dial (spin to each click number; Hacking/stethoscope widen the *click* cue)
;   * KEYPAD-> Mastermind deduction (▲▼ change a digit, [Enter] submit; read exact/partial)
;   * CASE  -> e-lock hack (route the ◄►▲▼ sequence under a soft timer; NON-MODAL — proximity pauses it)
;   * VAULT -> drill tension gauge ([Enter] to clear a JAM; NON-MODAL — it grinds while guards would close in)
; See docs/tasks/07_minigames.md.

